<section class="opa-section opa-light opa-timeline" id="timeline">
  <div class="opa-container">
    <p class="opa-eyebrow opa-reveal">14 Nights</p>
    <h2 class="opa-h1 opa-reveal">From Night 01<br><span class="opa-italic">to a live product</span>.</h2>
    <p class="opa-lead opa-reveal">Each night has one objective and a binary done-check. Walk the line.</p>

    <ol class="opa-timeline__list" data-opa-timeline>
      <div class="opa-timeline__spine" aria-hidden="true"><span data-opa-timeline-fill></span></div>

      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="01">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 01</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Define the operator</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: you can name the person you serve in one sentence.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="01">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 02</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Choose the format</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: PDF, template pack, or prompt pack &mdash; decided.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="02">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 03</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Open conversations</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: three scheduled, two completed.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="02">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 04</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Synthesize the pattern</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: one sentence the audience said back to you.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 05</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Build draft v1</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: skeleton outline + 30% of content drafted.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 06</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Apply the rule of one</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: anything not pulling weight is cut.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 07</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">First reader pass</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: one human read it and gave feedback.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 08</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Revision against feedback</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: v1 &rarr; v2 changes shipped.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 09</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Package + cover</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: final file ready to upload.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 10</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Pricing decision</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: single price set with reasoning.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 11</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Store live</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: Gumroad / Payhip / Shopify page published.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 12</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Outreach prep</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: list of 20 humans + script.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 13</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Soft launch</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: first 5 messages sent. Track responses.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="opa-timeline__row opa-reveal" data-phase="03">
        <span class="opa-timeline__n">Night 14</span>
        <div class="opa-timeline__body">
          <p class="opa-timeline__obj">Public launch</p>
          <p class="opa-timeline__done">Done when: product live, link shared, sale or no sale &mdash; data.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{ "name": "Timeline", "settings": [], "presets": [{ "name": "Timeline" }] }
{% endschema %}
